title: Add support for gpt-4o-2024-08-06 to multi modal llms
body:
# Description

Adding support for the newly released gpt-4o-2024-11-20 model in multi modal llms.
This model has already been added to llm, but has not been added to multi modal llms


Fixes # (issue)
